title: Arista Switches: Voltage Sensors
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/arista
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the voltage sensors of Arista Networks switches via
 the SNMP ENTITY-SENSOR-MIB. Sensors reporting their unit as Volts are
 monitored.

 Lower warning and critical levels can be configured via the rule "Arista
 Voltage" (default 50 V / 50 V). The sensor's own status is evaluated as
 well: status 1 is {OK}, status 2 is {WARN}.

discovery:
 One service is created for each sensor reporting its unit as Volts.

item:
 The entity description of the sensor.
